parameters:
Housewife Jelly: Sigh... I really want to do something about
that one in the pantry.
Housewife Jelly: Finally, a helping hand has come!
Clea: Where is the giant snake?

Housewife Jelly: Even though it was big, it was surprisingly
fast... It escaped into the underground food storage!
Thief Nora: Eh, aren't the guards coming?

Housewife Jelly: One of the most untrustworthy things in
this town! The other one is the rumor that another crystal
has been excavated.

Housewife Jelly: The food storage should be in a mess. You
can move things as you like, so please make sure to defeat
it!

Housewife Jelly: I asked you because I can't sleep
peacefully because of the giant snake, you know.
Homemaker Jelly: I heard a loud noise, but are you okay?
Thief Nora: Yes, I've properly defeated the snake!

Homemaker Jelly: I'm really grateful! With this, it'll be
fine even if my husband comes back anytime.

Homemaker Jelly: This is a reward and a token of gratitude.
Please use it if you get injured.
Thief Nora: Thank you very much!

Housewife Jelly: These young ladies are amazing! The men in
the neighborhood should learn from them!
